A student has 
  a control_number string, 
  a course_number string. 

A course is a string.

To run:
  Start up.  
  Loop.
    write "BIENVENIDO AL CMS" to the console.
    write "Selecciona la opción a realizar" to the console.
    skip one line on the console.
    write "3. Calificar" to the console.
    write "2. Borrar inscripción" to the console.
    write "1. Inscribir" to the console.
    write "0. Salir" to the console.
    skip one line to the console.   
    write "Opción: " to the console without advancing. 
    read a string from the console.
    if the string is "0", break.
    if the string is "1", inscribir.
    if the string is "2", borrar.
    if the string is "3", calificar.
  Repeat.
  Shut down.

To skip one line on the console;
To skip one line to the console:
  write "" to the console.
